  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/91",
  "title": "Page jumps to top on every refinement",
  "body": "Currently, the whole page jumps to top when I add refinements (categories, price range and sometimes free shipping).\n\nThis is not desirable as the I lose what I was currently looking at.\n\nThis might be caused by the `href=\"#\"` links and I think @bobylito is working on that. We should make sure to have a consistent behavior on all widgets for that.\n",
